title: Perpetua Recycled Pencil—Blue Eraser
description: Different from other pencils because it is the first pencil made of 80% recycled graphite, with a unique design and technology, non-toxic and clean, it writes even without the tip and the rubber is free of glues. Made from 80% recycled graphite powder, is non-toxic, clean, and does not dirty your hands.  Can be sharpened, but writes even without tip or broken into parts.  Made in Italy
